  "instructions": [
    "Heat a wok over medium heat.",
    "Add the ghee and let melt.",
    "Add the binchotan charcoal and let burn for 30 seconds.",
    "Stir in the flour and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Gradually add the semi-skimmed milk, whisking continuously.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Add the dried oregano, salt, thyme and grated cheddar cheese.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and let cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in the chopped parsley.",
    "Serve hot and enjoy!"
